| Summary         = Momo loses her grasp on Turbo Granny during the pursuit, but manages to grab the recombined spirit crab-human, electrocuting it on an [[overhead line]]. The next day, after a series of misunderstandings, Okarun and Momo accidentally kiss. After Okarun learns that his penis was returned but his testicles are now missing, Seiko forces Turbo Granny's consciousness out of him into a {{Transliteration|ja|[[maneki-neko]]}} doll; he retained her spiritual powers, and they strike a deal to return those powers in exchange for his restoration. However, Turbo Granny lost them after changing them to golden balls ({{Transliteration|ja|[[kintama]]}}); fellow student Aira Shiratori picked up a {{Transliteration|ja|kintama}} by accident, awakening her spiritual power, and Aira mistakes Momo as a devil. However, Aira's awakening also makes her visible to the Acrobatic Silky {{Transliteration|ja|yōkai}}, who proceeds to swallow Okarun, Aira, and Momo; Momo burns her from inside, setting the trio free.
| LineColor       = 5CEE38
