| Summary         = The athletic Evil Eye/Jiji targets Momo and Turbo Granny, but Okarun protects them and throws Momo to the surface, where she sets the house aflame. Okarun and Evil Eye fight as the wounded worm spews venom; as the fire department pours water on the house, the worm surfaces and is consumed in sunlight, then regurgitates the Kito family. As the volcano erupts, Momo uses the worm's body as a hose to divert water onto the lava. The {{Transliteration|ja|Tsuchinoko}} shrine priest defends her from the Kito matriarch. All three unite to face the Evil Eye; he is delayed by the mantis shrimp and then defeated by Seiko and Taro. Taro seals the Evil Eye inside his shell, which is lined with {{Transliteration|ja|[[ofuda]]}} amulets. Chiqutita continues fighting the lava from aboard their [[flying saucer]] and lifts a ball of worm phlegm from underground, which protected Okarun and Turbo Granny. Sharing a meal of {{Transliteration|ja|[[oden]]}} together, Seiko discovers that hot water will turn the Evil Eye back to Jiji, and cold water reverts to Evil Eye.
| LineColor       = 5CEE38
